<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4114.4.7>
    bibo:endPage "484" ;
    bibo:issue "4" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "477" ;
    bibo:volume "4114" ;
    dc:creator "Narita, João Paulo Z.; De Moraes, Gilberto J." ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Epicriopsis Berlese (Acari: Mesostigmata: Ameroseiidae) from Brazil, with a key to the world species of the genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256574>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256575> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256574>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Epicriopsis atuberculatus n. sp. female. 1. Chelicera; 2. Epistome; 3. Ventral view of gnathosoma; 4. Dorsum of idiosoma; 5. Venter of idiosoma; 6. Proximal section of peritreme and associated structures (a: unsclerotised cuticle; b: peritrematic shield). Pores and lyrifissures enlarged to allow their differentiation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/256574/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256575>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 10. Epicriopsis atuberculatus n. sp. male. 7. Chelicera; 8. Dorsum of idiosoma; 9 and 10. Venter of idiosoma of two paratypes. Pores and lyrifissures enlarged to allow their differentiation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/256575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

